
= classx

== Synopsis

  require 'classx'
  class Point < ClassX
    has :x, :is => :ro, :kind_of => Fixnum, :required => true
    has :y, :is => :ro, :kind_of => Fixnum, :required => true
  end

  class Point3D < Point
    has :z, :is => :ro, :kind_of => Fixnum, :required => true
  end

  Point.new(:x => 30, :y => 40)  #=> <# Point @x=30, @y=40 >
  Point3D.new(:x => 30, :y => 40, :z => 50)  #=> <# Point3D @x=30, @y=40, @z=50 >

== Description
perl's Moose like Class interface.

== Installation

=== Archive Installation

	rake install

=== Gem Installation

	gem install classx

